<h2>Cut Your Costs in Half</h2>
  <p>A carpool can be a great way to go! Youâ€™ll cut the cost of commuting in half and save wear and tear on your car. CT<strong>rides</strong> has a free online ridematching program that shows you whoâ€™s going your way. You might even find coworkers in your neighborhood! Take a look at <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140818092917/http://www.nuride.com/" target="_blank">www.nuride.com</a>.</p>
  <p>And whatever way you decide to go, sign up for FREE Commuter Rewards! Earn points for every ride you share and get great discounts and coupons on things you use everyday! <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20140818092917/http://www.nuride.com/ctrides" target="_blank">Check it out!</a></p>
