                	<h3>Free Trial Ride</h3>
					<p>CT<strong>rides</strong> offers free rides to give commuters a chance to try and experience the convenience of bus and vanpool travel.</p>
					<p>The 10-trip bus pass or vanpool is for first time commuters.</p> 
                    <p>Call: 1-877-CT<strong>rides</strong> (1-877-287-4337)</p>
